231
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:01,250
Karin-chan.

232
00:16:01,750 --> 00:16:02,210
Áno?

233
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:03,880
Už je neskoro.

234
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:06,090
Môžeš ísť.

235
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:07,090
Okay.

236
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:10,220
Usui-kun ťa aj dnes odprevadí domov.

237
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,800
Už som sa ho na to spýtal.

238
00:16:12,970 --> 00:16:13,470
Okay.

239
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:21,980
<I>Vedúci, ani neviete čo ste spôsobili...</I>

240
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:23,940
<I>Z tohto môžu byť problémy.</I>

241
00:16:24,350 --> 00:16:28,650
<I>Nemôžem sa k Usui-ovi priblížiť, kým nevymyslím nejaké protiopatrenie.</I>

242
00:16:32,150 --> 00:16:35,240
<I>Ale ja som sa rozhodla urobiť ho šťastným!</I>

243
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:39,660
<I>Najdôležitejšie je dozvedieť sa čo najviac o subjekte! Čo najviac!</I>

244
00:16:41,620 --> 00:16:45,170
<I>Ale ak sa mi krv znovu vzbúri a začnem krvácať, neprežijem to!</I>

245
00:16:52,130 --> 00:16:53,510
Prepáč, že si musel čakať.

246
00:16:54,470 --> 00:16:54,930
V poriadku.

247
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:10,320
<I>No tak, spýtaj sa ho, Karin! Spýtaj sa, kedy je Usui-kun najšťastnejší!</I>

248
00:17:12,190 --> 00:17:12,900
Um...
Um...

249
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:17,280
Usui-kun, ty prvý.

250
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:18,280
Oh.

251
00:17:19,280 --> 00:17:20,540
Um, er...

252
00:17:21,870 --> 00:17:24,830
To je v poriadku, Tokitou mi dala svoju desiatu.

253
00:17:26,710 --> 00:17:32,010
Zabudol som jej to vrátiť, tak sa chcem
spýtať, či jej to nedáš.

254
00:17:33,590 --> 00:17:34,300
Môžeš?

255
00:17:39,470 --> 00:17:39,930
Um...

256
00:17:40,970 --> 00:17:41,600
To...

257
00:17:42,810 --> 00:17:44,270
...bola moja desiata.

258
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:47,350
Oh, tvoja?

259
00:17:48,980 --> 00:17:52,860
Bolo to výborné. Maaka, tvoja mama varí dobre.

260
00:17:53,490 --> 00:17:54,110
Um...

261
00:17:55,110 --> 00:17:56,530
Ja som to robila.

262
00:17:57,450 --> 00:17:57,990
Vážne.

263
00:17:59,120 --> 00:17:59,910
Bolo to vynikajúce.

264
00:18:02,950 --> 00:18:05,830
Musím ešte nakúpiť, zvládneš to odtiaľto?

265
00:18:07,540 --> 00:18:08,330
Okay...

266
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:09,540
Zatiaľ.

267
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:15,840
Tadaima.

268
00:18:17,130 --> 00:18:20,220
Onee-chan, už si zistila čo je šťastie?

269
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:24,430
Ešte nie. Ale stále na tom pracujem!

270
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,140
Určite.

271
00:18:26,230 --> 00:18:26,940
Oh.

272
00:18:27,140 --> 00:18:29,150
Ja som to hneď pochopil.

273
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:30,060
Áno, to určite.

274
00:18:30,860 --> 00:18:35,990
Je to niečo čomu ty nechápeš, takže ti to vysvetlím...

275
00:18:36,570 --> 00:18:38,660
Takže? Moje šťastie je...

276
00:18:38,660 --> 00:18:40,070
Úplne čisté.

277
00:18:40,820 --> 00:18:42,200
Usui-kun je úžasný.

278
00:18:42,620 --> 00:18:44,740
Aj keď je to chlapec, umyl to dobre.

279
00:18:47,370 --> 00:18:48,250
Bolo to vynikajúce.

280
00:18:51,250 --> 00:18:52,960
On vyzeral šťastný.

281
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:55,960
Ak sa nad tým zamyslím...

282
00:18:56,460 --> 00:18:59,010
..krv sa mi nevzbúrila...

283
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:03,510
Keď Usui-kun zjedol moje jedlo, nešťastie zmizlo?

284
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,640
Jedlo?!

285
00:19:06,850 --> 00:19:09,520
...a pretože je to tak, šťastie je...

286
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:10,520
Pochopila som

287
00:19:12,270 --> 00:19:12,980
Vážne?

288
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:16,190
Presne! Jedlo je šťastie!

289
00:19:18,360 --> 00:19:22,160
Výborne! Takže mu každý deň jedno urobím!

290
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:26,370
Haló?

291
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:29,500
Maki? Práve som ti chcela zavolať!

292
00:19:30,710 --> 00:19:33,920
Máš doma nejaké recepty?

293
00:19:34,380 --> 00:19:35,960
Daj mi nejaké, no tak, no tak?

294
00:19:37,420 --> 00:19:38,050
Dobre.

295
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:40,340
Zajtra ti ich prinesiem.

296
00:19:41,130 --> 00:19:41,760
Prosím!

297
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:43,720
Áno.

298
00:19:45,220 --> 00:19:45,810
Rozumiem.

299
00:19:47,390 --> 00:19:48,770
Takže, uvidíme sa zajtra.

300
00:19:50,230 --> 00:19:50,980
Ojasumi.
(Dobrú noc)

301
00:19:52,810 --> 00:19:55,730
Dobre! Teraz si budem môcť vybrať zo širokej ponuky jedál!

302
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:56,360
Huh?

303
00:19:57,570 --> 00:20:00,280
Ale čo má vlastne Usui-kun rád.

304
00:20:01,320 --> 00:20:03,450
Mala som sa spýtať!

305
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,580
Som taký blbec, blbec, blbec!

306
00:20:09,450 --> 00:20:10,790
Tadaima!

307
00:20:11,670 --> 00:20:12,830
Vitaj, Mama.

308
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:16,710
Idem neskoro, lebo som mala množstvo pohovorov.

309
00:20:17,460 --> 00:20:18,590
Prepáč mi to.

310
00:20:19,550 --> 00:20:20,260
Ako to šlo?

311
00:20:20,970 --> 00:20:22,880
Zle, všetky zle.

312
00:20:25,050 --> 00:20:25,510
Oh.

313
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:29,310
Oh nie! Kenta, nemusíš sa trápiť!

314
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:32,690
Pokaziť jeden alebo dva pohovory...

315
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:34,400
...alebo tri či štyri...

316
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:37,860
...prípadne päť alebo šesť je normálne.

317
00:20:38,020 --> 00:20:40,570
Som si istá, že som sa aj tak na tú prácu nehodila.

318
00:20:41,110 --> 00:20:45,120
To je v poriadku! Zajtra si už nájdem skvelú prácu!

319
00:20:47,780 --> 00:20:49,240
Ak si šťastná, mama.

320
00:20:49,450 --> 00:20:52,540
Huh? Ale ja som stále šťastná.

321
00:20:57,090 --> 00:20:58,090
Mám ťa!

322
00:20:58,750 --> 00:21:00,340
Čo si taký prekvapený?

323
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,180
Nemožné...

324
00:21:08,470 --> 00:21:08,850
Huh?

325
00:21:10,060 --> 00:21:12,310
To sú kúsance od Maaky.
(Sorry za výraz)

326
00:21:13,060 --> 00:21:14,600
Maaka je upír?

327
00:21:16,690 --> 00:21:17,400
Nemožné.

328
00:21:17,770 --> 00:21:18,360
Nie?

329
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:21,650
Tak, čo urobím?

330
00:21:22,610 --> 00:21:25,410
To vyzerá dobre. Oh, to tiež!

331
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:57,270
Kimi ni au toki ga ichiban ureshii
It's when I see you that I'm the happiest.

332
00:21:58,310 --> 00:22:04,570
Kimi ni au toki ga ichiban kurushii kedo
It's when I see you that it hurts the most, but...

333
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:12,950
Afuredasu omoi wo moshi uchiagete shimattara, ne
I wonder what kind of future would come...

334
00:22:13,450 --> 00:22:18,500
Donna mirai ga kuru ka na
...If I let this overflowing feeling out.

335
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:23,050
Suki na hito ni suki to ieru
Being able to tell the person you love that you love him...

336
00:22:23,300 --> 00:22:26,760
Kirameku tokubetsu na yume
...would be a special sparkling dream...

337
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:30,600
Kizu tsuku koto mo nanimo osorezu
...If you can start runnning without being afraid...

338
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:34,470
kakedashite yukeru no nara
...of getting hurt or anything else.

339
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:38,230
Suki na hito ni suki to ieru
If I can tell the person I love that I love him...

340
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:41,940
Sono hi wa atarashii BIRTHDAY
...then that day would become my new birthday...

341
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:46,070
Kinou to chigau watashi ni natte
...and I'll become a me different from yesterday...

342
00:22:46,110 --> 00:22:54,790
mayowazu ni tokihanasu yo MY LOVE FOR YOU
...and set free my love for you without it getting lost.

343
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:07,970
Môžem ti to povedať, Onii-chan?

344
00:23:09,010 --> 00:23:11,510
aká je sestrina pravá podoba...

345
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:16,350
Nabudúce v Karin: Byť odhalená je ponižujúce.

346
00:23:17,850 --> 00:23:19,350
Ona už znovu zaspala.

